sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant C as 🎯 Claude (PM)
    participant SI as session-init
    participant CE as ⚡ ContextEngine
    participant M as 🧠 Memory
    participant D as 🤖 Daemon
    participant PB as 🔨 Pi Builder
    participant PR as 👀 Pi Reviewer
    participant PF as 🔧 Pi Fixer
    participant SC as 🔄 step-closure

    Note over U,SC: === Session Initialization ===
    U->>C: Task description
    C->>SI: session-init(task_description)
    SI->>CE: principle_activate(domain_hint)
    CE-->>SI: 12 principles (domain-filtered)
    SI->>CE: context_supply(task_description)
    CE->>M: memory_recall (3-way retrieval)
    M-->>CE: Core + related memories
    CE-->>SI: 🔵Core + 🟡Related context
    SI->>M: memory_store (session start)
    SI-->>C: principles + scarf_baseline + domain_health

    Note over U,SC: === Task Execution ===
    C->>C: Decompose task
    C->>D: task_enqueue (via memory_store tags)
    D->>D: Zero-token poll (SQLite)
    D->>PB: Spawn Pi Builder
    PB->>CE: memory_recall + context_supply
    CE-->>PB: Context injection
    PB->>PB: Implement (TDD)
    PB->>M: memory_store (completion)
    PB->>D: /notify (task done)

    D->>D: Detect task:done tag
    D->>PR: Spawn Pi Reviewer
    PR->>CE: context_supply(task_type="code_review")
    CE-->>PR: Review context
    PR->>PR: Code review
    PR->>C: Review report

    alt Review Passed
        C->>C: task_verify → approved
        C->>SC: step-closure(mode="full")
        SC->>SC: Principle alignment check
        SC->>SC: SCARF 5-dim introspection
        SC->>SC: Hormone update
        SC->>SC: Trust score linkage
        SC->>M: Reflection memory store
        SC-->>C: CEI composite index
    else Review Rejected
        C->>D: task rejected → auto-dispatch
        D->>PF: Spawn Pi Fixer
        PF->>PF: Fix issues
        PF->>M: memory_store (fix)
        PF->>D: /notify → re-review
    end

    Note over U,SC: === Background (Continuous) ===
    D->>D: Heartbeat monitoring (60s)
    D->>D: Task timeout recovery (5min)
    D->>D: 11-dimension audit (hourly)
    D->>M: memory_gc (weekly)
